        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>2000, 82/8300, 9400 and 5000 Models built between July 1993, and December 1993, may have broken
                    mounting tabs on the charge air cooler. This condition does not affect the performance of the charge
                    air cooler. If the tabs are broken, all that is holding the charge air cooler in place are the hoses
                    that attach it to the charge air cooler piping. To provide a secure mounting, a modification has
                    been developed that will secure the charge air cooler in place, and does not require weld repair of
                    the mounting tabs.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
